(IMPLEMENTATION) Model Architecture¶

Create a CNN to classify dog breed. At the end of your code cell block, summarize the layers of your model by executing the line:

    <your model's name>.summary()

Question 5: Outline the steps you took to get to your final CNN architecture and your reasoning at each step. Describe why you think the architecture is suitable for the current problem.

Answer: for Resnet50

  • I decided to use a GAP layer to lower the number of params compared to proceeding with a Max Pooling layer; its input_shape comes from what the layer expects during the training step.
  • The dense layer has 133 units because we have that many possible classes at the end of our models [i.e. 133 dog breeds].
  • It uses a softmax activation function so that our scores can be turned into probabilities at the end of the process.
In [146]:
### Define your architecture.

model_Resnet50 = Sequential();

model_Resnet50.add(GlobalAveragePooling2D(input_shape=(1, 1, 2048)))

model_Resnet50.add(Dense(133, activation='softmax'))

  Epoch  Epoch  Epoch  Epoch  Epoch   Epoch Epoch Epoch Epoch Epoch Epoch Epoch Epoch Epoch Epoch Epoch Epoch Epoch Epoch Epoch Epoch Epoch
